    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors and determined that the simulation evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device at MRL 2. The majority of assessed factors meet or exceed required levels. The discretization error factor was reviewed and the two-mesh comparison was judged adequate given the conservative nature of the hemolysis model and the margin observed in the RH metric (all points RH < 0.85). Assurance level Medium reflects the overall completeness of the evidence package and the favorable validation outcomes across all five operating points.",
